ledge of liquor, spirits, and beer Bartending license Ensure accuracy of cash drawer Knowledge of company procedures Knowledge of food safety Bartender related job titles: Barback Barmaid Mixologist Barkeeper Tapster Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
